# Backend Naming Convention Rules (C#)

## Controller Layer
- Folder: `Controllers`
- File naming: `[function]Controller.cs` 
- Class naming: `[Function]Controller`

## Business Logic Layer (BL)
- Folder: `BL`
- File naming: 
  - Interface: `I[function]BL.cs` (e.g. `IUserBL.cs`)
  - Implementation: `[function]BL.cs`
- Class naming:
  - Interface: `I[Function]BL` 
  - Implementation: `[Function]BL`

## Data Layer (DL)
- Folder: `DL`
- File naming:
  - Interface: `I[function]DL.cs`
  - Implementation: `[function]DL.cs`
- Class naming:
  - Interface: `I[Function]DL`
  - Implementation: `[Function]DL`

## Flow Pattern
Controller -> BL (qua interface) -> DL (qua interface) -> Database
